Welcome to AliOS Things Linux Edition !!!
Linkkit is a important component in AliOS Things Linux Edition.
please visit: https://living.aliyun.com/ or https://living-global.aliyun.com/ for more information.

1 startup

1.1 build linkkit

    bitbake linkkit

1.2 add linkkit into image

modify local.conf:

    vim conf/local.conf

add this line:

    IMAGE_INSTALL_append += " linkkit"

1.3 make image

    bitbake core-image-base